
apa yang ahrus di test :
- d0 test application domain : contohnya testing api, logic
- dont test generated code : ini dikarnakan tidak dibuat oleh kita, ini dibuat oleh sistem
- dont test issue caught by compiler
- dont test dependexcy or third party code
- do test application user interce by automating unit test

unit testing :
- performed in memory
- dont access network
- dont hit database
- dont use the file system
- unit testing about more domain testing, domain : seperti transfer, membeli barang, dan lain lain

apa yang membuat bagus unit test: 
- independent, dapat berjalan tanpa wifi koneksi contohnya. tidak bergantung pada yang lain.
- automatic 
- repeatable
- readable

INTEGRATION TEST:
- component are combined and tested together to evaluate interractions between them
- intergration test goes through real world scenarios of how the whole system wil work
- the fincal sterp is acceptacne testing. the client tests the software on actual hardware using actual data

ACCEPTANCE TESTING :
- accetance testing is testing performed to satisfy the bisuness criteria
- acceptance testing is perfoemaed on business requirement and needs
- acceptance testing is perfoemed by client or the end user


PERFORMANCE TESTING
- Throughtput : the number of request / transactions processed by the application in specified time duration. insert data ke database dengan total 10.000 data dalam waktu 1 detik
- Response Time : is defined as the delay between the point of request and thie fierst response
- Tuning : is an iterative process that we use to identify and elimate bottlenecks in the application
- Benchmarking : is the practice of comaring business proccess and performance metrics to industry bests and best practices from other companies


